{"lang":"ko","stage":6,"title":"longer everyday sentences","sentences":[{"t":"파티에 갔어요.","en":"I went to the party.","r":"patie gasseoyo.","a":"n_142ce41822b5.mp3"},{"t":"파티에 와요?","en":"Are you coming to the party?","r":"patie wayo?","a":"n_ff2ed25dc1c7.mp3"},{"t":"버스 지금 와요.","en":"The bus is coming now.","r":"beoseu jigeum wayo.","a":"n_fd912d3e7935.mp3"},{"t":"이 근처에 살아요.","en":"I live close to here.","r":"i geuncheoe sarayo.","a":"n_14d73af97036.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 다 알아요.","en":"He knows everyone.","r":"geu saram da arayo.","a":"n_366f9faf5f48.mp3"},{"t":"머리가 아파요.","en":"My head hurts.","r":"meoriga apayo.","a":"n_2730a6974bf2.mp3"},{"t":"오 분 안에 와요.","en":"It arrives in five minutes.","r":"o bun ane wayo.","a":"n_671891f357d4.mp3"},{"t":"사실대로 말하는 게 좋아요.","en":"You should tell the truth.","r":"sasildaero malhaneun ge joayo.","a":"n_7079e97a2296.mp3"},{"t":"좀 쉬는 게 좋아요.","en":"You should rest a little.","r":"jom swineun ge joayo.","a":"n_03682b30447e.mp3"},{"t":"이거 정말 맛있어요.","en":"This is delicious.","r":"igeo jeongmal masisseoyo.","a":"n_7302a3704ce2.mp3"},{"t":"더는 못 기다리겠어요.","en":"I can't wait any longer.","r":"deoneun mot gidarigesseoyo.","a":"n_86dc36694eaa.mp3"},{"t":"어떻게 되는지 보고 싶어요.","en":"I want to see what happens.","r":"eotteoke doeneunji bogo sipeoyo.","a":"n_bdb4b44d4d97.mp3"},{"t":"한 시간 뒤에 올게요.","en":"I'll be back in an hour.","r":"han sigan dwie olgeyo.","a":"n_5c411cf32d4f.mp3"},{"t":"마실 거 좀 줘요.","en":"I want something to drink.","r":"masil geo jom jwoyo.","a":"n_ac2ef3186421.mp3"},{"t":"뭐 마실래요?","en":"What are you going to drink?","r":"mwo masillaeyo?","a":"n_1eaa0e24c5f2.mp3"},{"t":"물 마실게요.","en":"I'll have water.","r":"mul masilgeyo.","a":"n_78e429d80e1d.mp3"},{"t":"이번엔 제가 낼게요.","en":"This time I'm paying.","r":"ibeonen jega naelgeyo.","a":"n_27579539f280.mp3"},{"t":"오른쪽에 있어요.","en":"It's on the right.","r":"oreunjjoge isseoyo.","a":"n_cbb302604a26.mp3"},{"t":"오른쪽으로 돌아요.","en":"Turn right.","r":"oreunjjogeuro dorayo.","a":"n_fd2725dbc018.mp3"},{"t":"택시 타