mp3"},{"t":"어제 맛있는 거 먹었어요.","en":"I ate something tasty yesterday.","r":"eoje masinneun geo meogeosseoyo.","a":"n_aebcdb930346.mp3"},{"t":"시작할 준비됐어요.","en":"I'm ready to start.","r":"sijakal junbidwaesseoyo.","a":"n_5a93e8be91f7.mp3"},{"t":"요리 좀 할 줄 알아요.","en":"I know how to cook a little.","r":"yori jom hal jul arayo.","a":"n_9fdfb98528d5.mp3"},{"t":"그거 아무도 안 사요.","en":"Nobody wants to buy that.","r":"geugeo amudo an sayo.","a":"n_c46f8e297226.mp3"},{"t":"저한테 오 유로 빚졌어요.","en":"You owe me five euros.","r":"jeohante o yuro bitjyeosseoyo.","a":"n_8647cafb173e.mp3"},{"t":"길 잘 알아요.","en":"I know the way well.","r":"gil jal arayo.","a":"n_b0ee52eb14c9.mp3"},{"t":"오늘 밤엔 안 나가요.","en":"I'm not going out tonight.","r":"oneul bamen an nagayo.","a":"n_2c63c1e57e5f.mp3"},{"t":"하나만 물어봐도 돼요?","en":"Can I ask one thing?","r":"hanaman mureobwado dwaeyo?","a":"n_f982e870cc65.mp3"},{"t":"이걸 어떻게 말하죠?","en":"How do I tell you this?","r":"igeol eotteoke malhajyo?","a":"n_fb1f9a90849e.mp3"},{"t":"이제 그 사람한테 뭐라고 하죠?","en":"What do I tell him now?","r":"ije geu saramhante mworago hajyo?","a":"n_9b7596a9e912.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 답을 알아요.","en":"He knows the answer.","r":"geu saram dabeul arayo.","a":"n_4a579b9ab5df.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람한테 고맙다고 했어요.","en":"I thanked her.","r":"geu saramhante gomapdago haesseoyo.","a":"n_63a6e99ae233.mp3"},{"t":"아직 준비 안 됐어요.","en":"We're not ready yet.","r":"ajik junbi an dwaesseoyo.","a":"n_27a6c69ce9d1.mp3"},{"t":"생각할 시간이 필요해요.","en":"I need time to think.","r":"saenggakal sigani piryohaeyo.","a":"n_91620decae55.mp3"},{"t":"우리 집은 작아요.","en":"My house is small.","r":"uri jibeun jagayo.","a":"n_bbcd747bae57.mp3"},{"t":"우리 집은 작아요.","en":"We have a small house.","r":"uri jibeun jagayo.","a":"n_bbcd747bae57.mp3"},{"t":"이 노래 좋아요.","en":"I like this song.","r":"i norae joayo.","a":"n_fe267bd73cf8.mp3"},{"t":"아무 말도 안 했어요.","en":"I didn't say anything.","r":"amu maldo an haesseoyo.","a":"n_ad617120149f.mp3"},{"t":"어떻게 되는지 이미 알아요.","en":"I already know how it works.","r":"eotteoke doeneunji imi arayo.","a":"n_347444f77e1a.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 일찍 일어나요.","en":"She gets up early.","r":"geu saram iljjik ireonayo.","a":"n_11c2e8c9a0ae.mp3"},{"t":"마실 거 뭐 있어요?","en":"What do you have to drink?","r":"masil geo mwo isseoyo?","a":"n_20692307876f.mp3"},{"t":"빵 좀 더 갖다줄 수 있어요?","en":"Can you bring me more bread?","r":"ppang jom deo gatdajul su isseoyo?","a":"n_75e274d443e2.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 집에서 지내요.","en":"She lives at home.","r":"geu saram jibeseo jinaeyo.","a":"n_365d36a638c0.mp3"},{"t":"여섯 시까지 일해요.","en":"I work until six.","r":"yeoseot sikkaji ilhaeyo.","a":"n_c0e6811f7912.mp3"},{"t":"핸드폰 팔고 싶어요.","en":"I want to sell my phone.","r":"haendeupon palgo sipeoyo.","a":"n_1358bfff14ee.mp3"},{"t":"표 어디서 사요?","en":"Where do I buy the ticket?","r":"pyo eodiseo sayo?","a":"n_b99bb790775c.mp3"},{"t":"목이 아파요.","en":"My throat hurts.","r":"mogi apayo.","a":"n_0e3a2a6ee463.mp3"},{"t":"제 친구예요.","en":"He's a friend of mine.","r":"je chinguyeyo.","a":"n_532b80e2a0af.mp3"},{"t":"저야말로 반가워요.","en":"The pleasure is mine.","r":"jeoyamallo bangawoyo.","a":"n_6edce1a9c720.mp3"},{"t":"오늘 진짜 바빠요.","en":"I'm really busy today.","r":"oneul jinjja bappayo.","a":"n_b43d888fae4f.mp3"},{"t":"제 친구들 행복해요.","en":"My friends are happy.","r":"je chingudeul haengbokaeyo.","a":"n_96cf514c95ea.mp3"},{"t":"떠나는 게 아쉬워요.","en":"I'm sad to leave.","r":"tteonaneun ge aswiwoyo.","a":"n_eac4ebd2733c.mp3"},{"t":"일찍 도착하는 일이 거의 없어요.","en":"I almost never arrive early.","r":"iljjik dochakaneun iri geoui eopseoyo.","a":"n_84539da077f8.mp3"},{"t":"지금 뭐 좀 먹어야 해요.","en":"We need to eat something now.","r":"jigeum mwo jom meogeoya haeyo.","a":"n_817c5d525a4f.mp3"},{"t":"초콜릿 정말 좋아해요.","en":"I love chocolate.","r":"chokollit jeongmal joahaeyo.","a":"n_81b19301a247.mp3"},{"t":"햇볕이 좋아요.","en":"I like the sun.","r":"haetbyeochi joayo.","a":"n_8d064ccbccb2.mp3"},{"t":"커피가 좋아요, 차가 좋아요?","en":"Do you prefer coffee or tea?","r":"keopiga joayo, chaga joayo?","a":"n_4608742a49c2.mp3"},{"t":"곧 보고 싶어요.","en":"I'd like to see you soon.","r":"got bogo sipeoyo.","a":"n_797f4c1b4f2c.mp3"},{"t":"지금은 말 못 해요.","en":"I can't tell you now.","r":"jigeumeun mal mot haeyo.","a":"n_33353ac27b72.mp3"},{"t":"오늘 진짜 일찍 왔어요.","en":"I got here really early today.","r":"oneul jinjja iljjik wasseoyo.","a":"n_f53b2964c229.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 우리랑 같이 와요.","en":"She's coming with us.","r":"geu saram urirang gachi wayo.","a":"n_a4920fe0b585.mp3"},{"t":"오 분 뒤에 나가요.","en":"We're leaving in five minutes.","r":"o bun dwie nagayo.","a":"n_75fd733db2bd.mp3"},{"t":"숙제 벌써 했어요?","en":"Did you do the homework yet?","r":"sukje beolsseo haesseoyo?","a":"n_6c4c7c5162b8.mp3"},{"t":"왜 그렇게 많이 물어봐요?","en":"Why do you ask so much?","r":"wae geureoke mani mureobwayo?","a":"n_e99ea752dd01.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 질문이 많아요.","en":"He asks a lot of questions.","r":"geu saram jilmuni manayo.","a":"n_1cc7bb5b9f45.mp3"},{"t":"아무한테도 아무 말 하기 싫어요.","en":"I don't want to tell anyone anything.","r":"amuhantedo amu mal hagi sireoyo.","a":"n_370e2069a8b1.mp3"},{"t":"오후에 봐요.","en":"See you this afternoon.","r":"ohue bwayo.","a":"n_0486280fab46.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 이름을 몰라요.","en":"I don't know his name.","r":"geu saram ireumeul mollayo.","a":"n_9c2ef8f0a7e5.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 제 사정을 알아요.","en":"She knows my story.","r":"geu saram je sajeongeul arayo.","a":"n_070778ec14f6.mp3"},{"t":"손이 아파요.","en":"My hand hurts.","r":"soni apayo.","a":"n_c9df67bad445.mp3"},{"t":"제 번호 줄게요.","en":"I'll give you my number.","r":"je beonho julgeyo.","a":"n_6b142fa39949.mp3"},{"t":"어떻게 하는지 보여 줘요.","en":"Show me how it's done.","r":"eotteoke haneunji boyeo jwoyo.","a":"n_fca42e6f2f93.mp3"},{"t":"약속했잖아요.","en":"I gave you my word.","r":"yaksokaetjanayo.","a":"n_d0d835bec1a8.mp3"},{"t":"좀 줄래요?","en":"Will you give me some?","r":"jom jullaeyo?","a":"n_a7ca1d3cf9ad.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람이 저를 어떻게 봤는지 봤어요?","en":"Did you see how he looked at me?","r":"geu sarami jeoreul eotteoke bwanneunji bwasseoyo?","a":"n_94739083a06b.mp3"}]}